name: Busy Sky
description:
Fly a sky balloon and try to stay afloat as long as possible. Leaving the screen means losing so you need to avoid getting to high or too low. Thankfully, dropping some of your excess weight helps with that. Don't get too comfortable though: your supply of weights is limited so you need to catch some of them balloons and also avoid smashing into birds and airplanes!

Controls: arrow keys and spacebar

Busy Sky was made for Mini Jam 122.

Music was generated by neural network AI called AIVA.
